    ::
    ++  dy-edit                                         ::  handle edit
      |=  cal/sole-change
      ^+  +>+>
      =^  dat  say  (~(transceive sole say) cal)
      ?:  |(?=(^ per) ?=(^ pux) ?=(~ pro))
        ~&  %dy-edit-busy
        =^  lic  say  (~(transmit sole say) dat)
