  ++  he-lens
    |=  com/command:lens
    ^+  +>
    =+  ^-  source/dojo-source
        =|  num/@
        =-  ?.  ?=($send-api -.sink.com)  ::  XX  num is incorrect
              sor
            :-  0
            :+  %as  `mark`(cat 3 api.sink.com '-poke')
            :-  1
            :+  %do
